# Git Branch Naming

When creating git branches, use **short, concise names** to minimize command-line clutter.

- ❌ `feature/add-user-authentication-with-oauth2-support`
- ✅ `feat/oauth2-auth`

- ❌ `fix/resolve-rendering-issue-in-diagram-viewer-component`
- ✅ `fix/diagram-render`

Keep branch names brief while still conveying intent.
